{"tid":1954681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那新聞] 亂港分子滯留國外求助中國大使館","createTime":"2020-04-02T04:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T08:39:42.000Z","uid":171094,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f9aa3881d57ac55de25e92988351b767ca0f8604","tid":1954681,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"BNO一早走咗，2千幾蚊搞得掂又唔見你班垃圾講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地BNO人冇話過要你支那大使幫囉好冇<br />\n<br />\n【#亂港分子滯留國外求助中國大使館#】新冠肺炎疫情在全球蔓延，各國實施出入境限制。儘管港府上月已呼籲市民避免所有非必要的外遊計劃，但仍有一批&ldquo;亂港分子&rdquo;執意前往秘魯旅遊，並在當地著名旅遊景點宣傳&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;。在秘魯宣布緊急狀態、關閉全部邊境後，這批港人才意識到問題，隨後求助香港入境處及中國駐秘魯大使館，希望幫助他們離開秘魯。香港市民狠批這幫人厚顏無恥，&ldquo;無事搞分裂，有事求國家&rdquo;。 #亂港分子向中國大使館求助#（環球網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNjLo4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNjLo4c.png&h=3eec26ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6ejtvT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6ejtvT.png&h=6704e3b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a575c1a2ed86b8db2c6b19e6b4ce6ab6c133293","tid":1954681,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"咪又係自己打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"af1ff540b17e11b06ab44123cf8177e12f35d556","tid":1954681,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"秘魯<br />\n我諗起項明生雙開FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e19bfde0241a3502c7ef31684d445c0660a96e","tid":1954681,"uid":69646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b66576dbe3620f940c52809bf99932bc3fac8e9","tid":1954681,"uid":10070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"邊到宣傳港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h